Package: wpor
Title: Weighted Pseudo-Outcome Regression
Version: 0.0.7
Authors@R:
    person("Aaron", "Fisher", , "afishe27@alumni.jh.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Aaron Fisher [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Aaron Fisher <afishe27@alumni.jh.edu>
Description: Implements the weighted pseudo-outcome regression methods discussed in <https://proceedings.mlr.press/v235/fisher24a.html>. For nuisance training methods, users can either input workflows from the 'tidymodels' set of packages or define their own training algorithms.
